{
  "texts": [
    "To address the above challenges, benchmarks and evaluation datasets are needed by the research communities.",
    "However, such resources are far from complete at present.",
    "To fully support personalization with LLMs, methodological and experimental frameworks need to be systematically established for all these perspectives.",
    "LLMs for personalizationIn the following sections, we delve into the potential of large language models for personalization, examining their evolution from simple use cases, like utilizing word knowledge as features, to more intricate integration with other tool modules to act as agents.",
    "Specifically, we focus on the progression of emergent capabilities, starting from basic world knowledge and understanding user intent, and advancing to high-level reasoning abilities."
  ]
}